      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/28/1/429/70",
      "text": [
        ": نحن العرب، وشيعتنا منا، وسائر الناس همج أو هبج. قال: قلت: وما الهمج؟ قال، الذباب، قلت: وما الهبج؟ قال: البق."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.basel-kadem": [
          "71.\tWith this chain of narrators, from Hasan bin Yusuf, from Uthman bin Jabala, from Dharees ibn Abdul-Malik, that he said: I heard Abu Abdillah, peace be upon him, say: We are Quraish, our party  are the Arabs and our enemies are the non-Arabs."
        ]
      }
